```plantuml
@startuml solenya-group_solenya
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #e0f7fa
  BorderColor #00796b
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor User

package "Solenya Framework" {
  rectangle "App" as App #b2ebf2
  rectangle "Component" as Component #b2ebf2
  rectangle "Router" as Router #b2ebf2
  rectangle "Validator" as Validator #b2ebf2
  rectangle "Storage" as Storage #b2ebf2
  rectangle "TimeTravel" as TimeTravel #b2ebf2
  rectangle "HTML Helper\nFunctions" as HTMLHelpers #b2ebf2
  rectangle "Widget Functions" as WidgetFunctions #b2ebf2
}

User --> App : Interacts with
App --> Component : Manages root component
Component --> HTMLHelpers : Creates virtual DOM
Component --> WidgetFunctions : Uses for form inputs
Component --> Validator : Validates input data
Component --> Storage : Serializes state
Component --> TimeTravel : Time travel debugging
App --> Router : Handles navigation
App --> Storage : Manages persistence

@enduml
```